cc7c4b4a-d4e4-4e8e-aaa0-cdfeaa35589a.title: Alrena
cc7c4b4a-d4e4-4e8e-aaa0-cdfeaa35589a.text:
Not too bad... I've just got some
troubles on my mind...

449ae0f0-7f7e-45be-8b93-dea210d5a6ed.title: <player>
449ae0f0-7f7e-45be-8b93-dea210d5a6ed.text:
Hello, Edmond has asked me to help find your
daughter.

ed01b75f-4dd6-49a6-9a11-1b2861acda23.title: Alrena
ed01b75f-4dd6-49a6-9a11-1b2861acda23.text:
Yes he told me. I've begun making your special gas
mask, but I need some dwellberries to finish it.

5d94ad8d-5aee-4fda-ac17-d3121c211769.title: Alrena
5d94ad8d-5aee-4fda-ac17-d3121c211769.text:
The best place to look is in McGrubor's Wood, just
west of Seers' Village.

b2b152d6-fead-4f8f-928d-798e366bbb0e.text: You give the dwellberries to Alrena.

02d16bde-4cd1-4563-a055-2c6d7fd68fad.text:
Alrena crushes the berries into a smooth paste. She then smears the
paste over a strange mask.

22f14c80-1e1b-415a-af4b-7a004eab0c6b.title: Alrena
22f14c80-1e1b-415a-af4b-7a004eab0c6b.text:
There we go, all done. While in West Ardougne you
must wear this at all times, or you could catch the
plague.

60d6f447-e028-40c1-86db-d43232ddec3c.title: Note
60d6f447-e028-40c1-86db-d43232ddec3c.text: next step to talk to Edmond

13a0c7a2-fc08-4019-b1e0-c8d78ed7e2b1.text: Alrena has given you a gas mask.

5294af2f-d673-496e-9f2b-cc23fddc23b0.title: Alrena
5294af2f-d673-496e-9f2b-cc23fddc23b0.text:
I'll make a spare mask for you in case you lose that
one. I'll hide it in the cupboard in case the mourners
come looking.

34118a16-b5dc-4b7b-a268-fd41fd6ff7f3.title: Alrena
34118a16-b5dc-4b7b-a268-fd41fd6ff7f3.text:
Hello darling, I think Edmond had a good idea of how
to get into West Ardougne, you should hear his idea.

f93a3ac4-0d67-4f37-b6d8-beea43814c61.title: <player>
f93a3ac4-0d67-4f37-b6d8-beea43814c61.text: Alright, I'll go and see him now.

bb03b6f9-2746-4f21-9ff4-80819abb3a3f.title: Alrena
bb03b6f9-2746-4f21-9ff4-80819abb3a3f.text: Hello darling, how's that tunnel coming along?

db48b6ff-5ebd-445d-be4f-8ef1d8a0882d.title: <player>
db48b6ff-5ebd-445d-be4f-8ef1d8a0882d.text:
I just need to soften the soil and then we'll start
digging.

1a340a14-62ed-44be-820f-0a9fbbd5adf2.title: Alrena
1a340a14-62ed-44be-820f-0a9fbbd5adf2.text: Well I'm sure you're quicker than Edmond.

94673fce-c8c4-406f-9f75-9edf0a6e222f.title: <player>
94673fce-c8c4-406f-9f75-9edf0a6e222f.text:
I just need to soften the soil a little more and then we'll
start digging.

b632d8d6-14a1-46cb-a573-0a32a491c674.title: Alrena
b632d8d6-14a1-46cb-a573-0a32a491c674.text:
One of the mourners has been sniffing around asking
questions about you and Edmond, you should keep an
eye out for him.

f6390191-66cc-4556-917b-b5f4ae31da40.title: Alrena
f6390191-66cc-4556-917b-b5f4ae31da40.text:
Also, don't forget about that spare gas mask if you need
it. It's hidden in the cupboard.

5a6a05eb-99b2-43af-ac0e-18627715c4ee.title: Alrena
5a6a05eb-99b2-43af-ac0e-18627715c4ee.text:
Hi, have you managed to get through to West
Ardougne?

815fa1d4-8bf8-425e-a05d-c36c3da02433.title: <player>
815fa1d4-8bf8-425e-a05d-c36c3da02433.text: Not yet, but I should be going soon.

ccb0250d-828f-497e-bb6a-96c335fa1a66.title: Alrena
ccb0250d-828f-497e-bb6a-96c335fa1a66.text:
Make sure you wear your mask while you're over
there! I can't think of a worse way to die.

7e3f55b5-9d4d-4ec2-91a6-444708f6563d.title: Alrena
7e3f55b5-9d4d-4ec2-91a6-444708f6563d.text:
Don't forget, I've got a spare one hidden in the
cupboard if you need it.

a0dd0fdc-0179-49dd-a27d-2653b1123921.title: Alrena
a0dd0fdc-0179-49dd-a27d-2653b1123921.text: Is there anything else I can do to help?

077d6258-1819-4a8b-a71e-cd33e01b0140.title: <player>
077d6258-1819-4a8b-a71e-cd33e01b0140.text: It's alright, I'll get her back soon.

0e6fe889-5dfe-4f75-9ed3-b7f5289d890c.title: Alrena
0e6fe889-5dfe-4f75-9ed3-b7f5289d890c.text:
That's the spirit, dear. Don't forget that there's a spare
gas mask in the cupboard if you need one.

b61e6d7a-a575-4bc8-b471-12e1ef3c2fc7.title: Alrena
b61e6d7a-a575-4bc8-b471-12e1ef3c2fc7.text: Is there anything else I can do to help?

76e30448-9e31-46fb-b6d0-637ddd45879d.title: <player>
76e30448-9e31-46fb-b6d0-637ddd45879d.text: Do you have a picture of Elena?

9f3d6c01-9e09-4db8-b4df-073795a3c1da.title: Alrena
9f3d6c01-9e09-4db8-b4df-073795a3c1da.text:
Yes. There should be one in the house somewhere. Let
me know if you need anything else.

557bdf73-e57a-45f7-b5db-70cfd48a1cba.title: Alrena
557bdf73-e57a-45f7-b5db-70cfd48a1cba.text:
That's the spirit, dear. Don't forget that there's a spare
gas mask in the cupboard if you need one.

cf4403c8-b08b-4698-8ff2-3791a86c325c.title: <player>
cf4403c8-b08b-4698-8ff2-3791a86c325c.text: It's alright, I'll get her back soon.

02ba6478-49bf-4f50-89ba-419159c43a1a.title: Alrena
02ba6478-49bf-4f50-89ba-419159c43a1a.text:
Thank you for rescuing my daughter! Elena has told
me of your bravery in entering a house that could have
been plague infected. I can't thank you enough!
